### ================================================================
### STEP 2. 객실 타입 등록 (호텔 등록 후 실행)
### 등록 시 자동 생성:
###   - RoomDateInventory (오늘~90일치, 21개)
###   - OtaChannelAllotment (야놀자/여기어때/요기서 각 10개)
### ================================================================

### [스탠다드룸] 12개
POST http://localhost:8080/api/room-types
Content-Type: application/json

{
"hotelId": 1,
"name": "스탠다드룸",
"grade": "STANDARD",
"basePrice": 100000,
"capacity": 2,
"totalCount": 12
}


